==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unscale
<hw>Un*scale"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>scale</ets>.]</ety> <def>To divest of scales; to
remove scales from.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>[An eagle] purging and <qex>unscaling</qex> her long-abused sight
at the fountain itself of heavenly radiance.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unscapable</ent>⟦br⟧
